{"tid":2335192,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我知自己配唔上人，點先可以靜靜地咁死左條心？","createTime":"2020-12-21T16:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T07:29:54.000Z","uid":207870,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6df78ee3d6088b140aa542856e68aaeb2162f5","tid":2335192,"uid":207870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"我想做夠100分，我想超級好咁對佢。<br />\n<br />\n呢一年，我唔開心個陣，佢一定係我身邊。<br />\n從來冇一個女仔咁真誠咁對我。<br />\n我一直以為我可以當佢朋友，但原來想保護佢嘅衝動係真架。<br />\n<br />\n但近排，佢係話「阿xxx都知我地無可能一齊嘅！」「幻想我哋拍拖？我哋點會一齊啊😂」<br />\n我仲末表白，佢唔知我真係沉咗佢船。<br />\n佢一直覺我係fk boy，大把女。<br />\n<br />\n我唔想失去一個咁好嘅朋友<br />\n我知我唔應該鐘意佢嘅....<br />\n<br />\n我哋日日都會吹水<br />\n我點樣先可以靜靜地咁死心？"},{"pid":"5668f13b8c2b3511db71aadd88ef8246ef93d922","tid":2335192,"uid":9392,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"死FK BOY死全家啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"9915d9f0a6f230e168a3814c0098264e9384e24e","tid":2335192,"uid":207870,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"5668f13b8c2b3511db71aadd88ef8246ef93d922","tid":2335192,"uid":9392,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"死FK BOY死全家啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"diu問題係我真係唔L係fk boy嘛。<br />\n仲係a0啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e677ea9d6e2bb61ac146a9dfc2cecf75574c7e37","tid":2335192,"uid":185565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:16:44.000Z","msg":"愈覆愈慢 約出嚟就話忙 好快收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f0cad87b2b860d345d4835324ca256d5e1fcfb","tid":2335192,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:16:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3600db4a9a396aa4839b6fb1b067e9e22f9b810","tid":2335192,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"問題係你有冇畀佢當你係異性先"},{"pid":"7b079416cdc4aeba48518d68cec2e6da77e9e296",